hieve coverage even without OAuth2.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Addressing native-image run failures**\\n\\nI’m looking into why the native-image run is failing. It seems that setup requires certain system properties, and the current test scaffold already has custom runtime arguments for version 5.0.0, which need to be updated for 5.0.1 as well. There’s some uncertainty about whether “sun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow” is actually a valid Java system property, but it looks like existing uses may interpret it correctly. I might need to ensure that tests provide a JSON output with actions and guidance to address this effectively.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"Vert.x Web Client 5.0.1 still depends on Netty 4.2.x, like 5.0.0, so Java 25 native-image runs likely need the same Netty/Unsafe runtime properties; no extra dependency or Docker service is required for meaningful WebClient coverage.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For native-test runtime, set system properties `-Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` and `-Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true` for version 5.0.1 as well. Tests can use an in-process Vert.x HTTP server on localhost; no external service is needed.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The `OAuth2WebClient` API references optional Vert.x auth artifacts; only add `io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2:5.0.1` if the generated tests intentionally cover OAuth2-specific APIs. Core WebClient, caching, sessions, forms, JSON, redirects, and streaming do not require it.\",\n    \"Local Gradle/native-image verification remains authoritative for whether the Java 25 Netty runtime properties are sufficient.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04c4e4241624d45e016a3ea39934c88190ac77b286ecd823f2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 34215, "output": 777, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34992, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782489996684, "responseId": "resp_04c4e4241624d45e016a3ea38d5c588190bae8038062779a7c"}, "toolResults": []}
